{
  "video_id": "I2vH0K8QiAE",
  "title": "Which is Better: Shadowing or Repeating?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 716.0,
      "end_time": 1616.0,
      "text": "- Which is better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 1616.0,
      "end_time": 2449.0,
      "text": "Shadowing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 2449.0,
      "end_time": 4267.0,
      "text": "Or listening, then repeating?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 4267.0,
      "end_time": 6850.0,
      "text": "(upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15364.0,
      "end_time": 16906.0,
      "text": "Hello, I'm Julian Northbrook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16906.0,
      "end_time": 19382.0,
      "text": "the Posh Punk of English education."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19382.0,
      "end_time": 20215.0,
      "text": "And in this video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20215.0,
      "end_time": 23121.0,
      "text": "I want to talk a little\nbit about shadowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23121.0,
      "end_time": 24366.0,
      "text": "There's a very good chance"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24366.0,
      "end_time": 26004.0,
      "text": "that you've seen the shadowing video"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26004.0,
      "end_time": 29325.0,
      "text": "that I made originally in 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29325.0,
      "end_time": 33492.0,
      "text": "and then re-uploaded to the\ncurrent YouTube channel in 2013."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34513.0,
      "end_time": 35346.0,
      "text": "(static)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 35346.0,
      "end_time": 37278.0,
      "text": "Today, I'm going to show you"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 37278.0,
      "end_time": 39793.0,
      "text": "how you can practise speaking English --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 39793.0,
      "end_time": 40626.0,
      "text": "(static)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40626.0,
      "end_time": 42819.0,
      "text": "Yes, that video is somewhat old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42819.0,
      "end_time": 45834.0,
      "text": "more than six years old, in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 45834.0,
      "end_time": 47690.0,
      "text": "at the time of recording this video."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 47690.0,
      "end_time": 50311.0,
      "text": "And to say that my thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 50311.0,
      "end_time": 53015.0,
      "text": "and not to mention my\nlearning, has changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 53015.0,
      "end_time": 57623.0,
      "text": "and progressed somewhat, would\nbe quite an understatement."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 57623.0,
      "end_time": 60411.0,
      "text": "So in this video and over the next few,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 60411.0,
      "end_time": 63422.0,
      "text": "I want to expand upon that video slightly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 63422.0,
      "end_time": 66924.0,
      "text": "and talk more about\nthe shadowing exercise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 66924.0,
      "end_time": 71233.0,
      "text": "the shadowing technique, and\nanswer some of your questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 71233.0,
      "end_time": 75414.0,
      "text": "On said shadowing video, I\ngot the following question."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75414.0,
      "end_time": 76254.0,
      "text": "\"Hi Julian."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 76254.0,
      "end_time": 78823.0,
      "text": "\"Shadowing is a really good method,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 78823.0,
      "end_time": 80446.0,
      "text": "\"but don't you think it's better"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80446.0,
      "end_time": 84080.0,
      "text": "\"not to copy the voice of\nthe speaker simultaneously?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 84080.0,
      "end_time": 86655.0,
      "text": "\"But to copy it after the speaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86655.0,
      "end_time": 88815.0,
      "text": "\"in order to hear your own voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88815.0,
      "end_time": 90245.0,
      "text": "\"What do you think?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90245.0,
      "end_time": 93179.0,
      "text": "Listening and then repeating is brilliant"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93179.0,
      "end_time": 96706.0,
      "text": "for working on your pronunciation."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96706.0,
      "end_time": 98690.0,
      "text": "When you listen and repeat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 98690.0,
      "end_time": 100301.0,
      "text": "you can hear what you're saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 100301.0,
      "end_time": 103688.0,
      "text": "and this just helps you to\nwork on the big problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 103688.0,
      "end_time": 105693.0,
      "text": "that you've got with your pronunciation."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 105693.0,
      "end_time": 109924.0,
      "text": "If you are unable to say\nsomething, you very quickly notice."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109924.0,
      "end_time": 114091.0,
      "text": "The drawback of that, however,\nis it's quite a slow process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 116245.0,
      "end_time": 120865.0,
      "text": "and you don't really get\nmuch bang for your buck."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120865.0,
      "end_time": 124770.0,
      "text": "That is, you really only just\nwork on your pronunciation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 124770.0,
      "end_time": 127277.0,
      "text": "and work out the\npronunciation of the words"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127277.0,
      "end_time": 129274.0,
      "text": "that you don't know, and that's it."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129274.0,
      "end_time": 130119.0,
      "text": "Finished."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130119.0,
      "end_time": 132315.0,
      "text": "Shadowing, on the other hand, is brilliant"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132315.0,
      "end_time": 136482.0,
      "text": "for working on what we call the\nphysical aspects of fluency."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138680.0,
      "end_time": 141632.0,
      "text": "That is, how your mouth muscles move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 141632.0,
      "end_time": 145406.0,
      "text": "your rhythm, your tone, your intonation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145406.0,
      "end_time": 148172.0,
      "text": "the speed at which you are speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 148172.0,
      "end_time": 152805.0,
      "text": "the pauses and the way that\nyou chunk your language."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152805.0,
      "end_time": 155638.0,
      "text": "There are many aspects to fluency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156586.0,
      "end_time": 160617.0,
      "text": "and what we call the, again,\nthe physical side of fluency."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160617.0,
      "end_time": 164198.0,
      "text": "Shadowing is brilliant\nfor working on those."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164198.0,
      "end_time": 168365.0,
      "text": "It is crap for working on\nthe creative side of fluency."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171313.0,
      "end_time": 175976.0,
      "text": "That is, the actual organising\nof the language in your mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175976.0,
      "end_time": 180439.0,
      "text": "because there is no creativity\ninvolved with shadowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180439.0,
      "end_time": 182720.0,
      "text": "You are listening to\nsomebody else speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182720.0,
      "end_time": 186674.0,
      "text": "and then you are mimicking what you hear."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186674.0,
      "end_time": 188437.0,
      "text": "However, this is why it's so good"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188437.0,
      "end_time": 189886.0,
      "text": "for working on the physical aspects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189886.0,
      "end_time": 193656.0,
      "text": "because the creative side\nof it is pushed out the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193656.0,
      "end_time": 196104.0,
      "text": "You don't need to worry about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196104.0,
      "end_time": 197103.0,
      "text": "So to put it simply,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197103.0,
      "end_time": 198791.0,
      "text": "I guess we'd say that shadowing is good"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 198791.0,
      "end_time": 201708.0,
      "text": "for building positive motor habits."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202771.0,
      "end_time": 205404.0,
      "text": "That is, you know, the\nphysical side of fluency."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205404.0,
      "end_time": 207657.0,
      "text": "Again, of the pronunciation,\nthe intonation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207657.0,
      "end_time": 210644.0,
      "text": "the rhythm at which you speak, the speed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 210644.0,
      "end_time": 214135.0,
      "text": "where you put the pauses,\nhow you chunk the language."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 214135.0,
      "end_time": 217219.0,
      "text": "You're not gonna get that by\njust listening to something"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217219.0,
      "end_time": 218795.0,
      "text": "and repeating it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 218795.0,
      "end_time": 221458.0,
      "text": "because you're not actually\nproducing the language"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 221458.0,
      "end_time": 223194.0,
      "text": "in real time."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 223194.0,
      "end_time": 226947.0,
      "text": "You're not being forced to\nmimic all of the subtleties"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226947.0,
      "end_time": 229264.0,
      "text": "of how the language is being pronounced."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 229264.0,
      "end_time": 232144.0,
      "text": "But again, the answer to the\nquestion, which is better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232144.0,
      "end_time": 234061.0,
      "text": "Really, it depends on what exactly it is"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 234061.0,
      "end_time": 235424.0,
      "text": "that you want to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235424.0,
      "end_time": 237119.0,
      "text": "Personally, I prefer shadowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 237119.0,
      "end_time": 241493.0,
      "text": "I don't really do listen\nand repeat for Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 241493.0,
      "end_time": 243401.0,
      "text": "because I don't really need to."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243401.0,
      "end_time": 247369.0,
      "text": "I don't really find any\nof the words of Japanese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 247369.0,
      "end_time": 249492.0,
      "text": "you know, that difficult to pronounce."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 249492.0,
      "end_time": 253271.0,
      "text": "Good chunking skills, rhythm, intonation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 253271.0,
      "end_time": 256237.0,
      "text": "however, is quite different\nbetween Japanese and English,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256237.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258751.00000000003,
      "text": "and that is something that\nI do need to practise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 258750.99999999997,
      "end_time": 260997.99999999997,
      "text": "and shadowing is, as far as I'm concerned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 260998.0,
      "end_time": 262960.0,
      "text": "the best way to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 262960.0,
      "end_time": 264302.0,
      "text": "If you have a question of your own,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 264302.0,
      "end_time": 266156.0,
      "text": "specifically about shadowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266156.0,
      "end_time": 268288.0,
      "text": "just ask it down in the Comments"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 268288.0,
      "end_time": 270707.0,
      "text": "and I will answer it in another video."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 270707.0,
      "end_time": 273768.0,
      "text": "I do plan to do a whole\nseries of these videos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 273768.0,
      "end_time": 275442.0,
      "text": "and probably the next one that I do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 275442.0,
      "end_time": 279649.0,
      "text": "I'll talk about where\nshadowing actually comes from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 279649.0,
      "end_time": 284412.0,
      "text": "cause it wasn't originally a\nlanguage learning exercise."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284412.0,
      "end_time": 286220.0,
      "text": "It was originally something else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 286220.0,
      "end_time": 290387.0,
      "text": "and we've just changed it into\na language learning exercise."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 291231.0,
      "end_time": 293276.0,
      "text": "Again, I'll talk about\nthat in another video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 293276.0,
      "end_time": 296993.0,
      "text": "as well as some more advanced\nvariations of shadowing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 296993.0,
      "end_time": 298544.0,
      "text": "as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 298544.0,
